---
import Layout from '../components/Layout.astro';
import Nav from '../components/Nav.astro';
---
<Layout title="The Lineup - Theme 2">
  <div class="bg-red-950 min-h-screen pb-12">
    <Nav />
    <main class="max-w-4xl mx-auto p-6 w-full mt-8">
      <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-6xl text-white font-display mb-8">Set Times</h1>
      
      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-8 mb-12">
        <div class="p-6 border-l-4 border-zinc-500 bg-zinc-800/60 backdrop-blur-md rounded-sm shadow-lg">
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-display text-white uppercase tracking-widest">The Venue</h2>
          <p class="text-zinc-300 mt-2 text-lg">
            Baltimore Soundstage<br />
            124 Market Pl<br />
            Baltimore, MD 21202
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="p-6 border-l-4 border-zinc-500 bg-zinc-800/60 backdrop-blur-md rounded-sm shadow-lg">
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-display text-white uppercase tracking-widest">Dress Code</h2>
          <p class="text-zinc-300 mt-2 text-lg italic">"Show-Ready Casual"</p>
          <p class="text-zinc-300 mt-2">
            Leave the ties and gowns at home. Wear what makes you feel like a VIP.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
      
      <div class="relative flex flex-col sm:flex-row bg-zinc-800/60 backdrop-blur-md border border-zinc-700 rounded-sm overflow-hidden shadow-2xl my-6">
        <div class="bg-zinc-900/60 px-6 py-8 flex flex-col justify-center items-center border-b sm:border-b-0 sm:border-r border-dashed border-zinc-700">
          <span class="text-center text-pink-400 text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-widest rotate-0 sm:-rotate-90 whitespace-nowrap">
            Trent & Shy<br /><br />Baltimore<br />Soundstage<br /><br />Oct 10, 2026
          </span>
        </div>
        <div class="p-8 flex-1">
          <h3 class="text-4xl text-white mb-1">Doors Open</h3>
          <p class="text-pink-300 font-bold uppercase tracking-wider text-sm mb-4">4:30 PM - The Lobby</p>
          <div class="text-zinc-300 leading-relaxed space-y-4">
            <p>Check your coat, grab a drink, and find your spot in the crowd. The pre-show bar is open.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="relative flex flex-col sm:flex-row bg-zinc-800/60 backdrop-blur-md border border-zinc-700 rounded-sm overflow-hidden shadow-2xl my-6">
        <div class="bg-zinc-900/60 px-6 py-8 flex flex-col justify-center items-center border-b sm:border-b-0 sm:border-r border-dashed border-zinc-700">
          <span class="text-center text-pink-400 text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-widest rotate-0 sm:-rotate-90 whitespace-nowrap">
            Trent & Shy<br /><br />Baltimore<br />Soundstage<br /><br />Oct 10, 2026
          </span>
        </div>
        <div class="p-8 flex-1">
          <h3 class="text-4xl text-white mb-1">The Main Act</h3>
          <p class="text-pink-300 font-bold uppercase tracking-wider text-sm mb-4">5:00 PM - Main Stage</p>
          <div class="text-zinc-300 leading-relaxed space-y-4">
            <p>The ceremony. Short, sweet, and heavy. Please silence your phones so you don't ruin the recording.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="relative flex flex-col sm:flex-row bg-zinc-800/60 backdrop-blur-md border border-zinc-700 rounded-sm overflow-hidden shadow-2xl my-6">
        <div class="bg-zinc-900/60 px-6 py-8 flex flex-col justify-center items-center border-b sm:border-b-0 sm:border-r border-dashed border-zinc-700">
          <span class="text-center text-pink-400 text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-widest rotate-0 sm:-rotate-90 whitespace-nowrap">
            Trent & Shy<br /><br />Baltimore<br />Soundstage<br /><br />Oct 10, 2026
          </span>
        </div>
        <div class="p-8 flex-1">
          <h3 class="text-4xl text-white mb-1">The Afterparty</h3>
          <p class="text-pink-300 font-bold uppercase tracking-wider text-sm mb-4">6:00 PM - Midnight</p>
          <div class="text-zinc-300 leading-relaxed space-y-4">
            <p>Dinner, drinks, and a very loud playlist. Bring your earplugs if you're sensitive to punching music—we’re turning it up to eleven.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </main>
  </div>
</Layout>